    <text id="F0101T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Mox writes a brief letter acknowledging the receipt of Jennie's last letter.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>
        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Jennie</name>
                </head>
                <opener>
                   
                    <salute>Dear Jennie </salute>
                </opener>

                <p>next time I write I will likely be able to give you some of my adventures in
                    Lovettsville for I have been detailed to work in the Lov. Bakery at that place.
                    I was down to town this afternoon and seen some very pretty ladies who will
                    likely get acquainted with this chicken before many weeks <orig reg="roll"
                    >role</orig> around But now Jennie you must not get jealous for I am resolved
                    not to fall in love with any of them, only just for the <orig reg="occasion"
                        >ocasion</orig>.</p>

                <p>You asked my advice as to how you should spend your next summer - I am really
                    surprised to think you would ask me what <del hand="h1">had to</del> to employ
                    yourself at when you are better able to judge for yourself. <orig reg="you know"
                        >you know your know</orig> your circumstances better than I do. So my advice
                    is to do the best you can<pb n="2"/> Now Jennie dear as it is getting late you
                    must excuse me for not writing more tonight I must go to the bakery early in the
                    morning so good night dear girl Good night</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute><orig reg="Very">Verry</orig> Affectionately Yours </salute>
                    <signed>Lucius P. Mox </signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Please write now to Lucius </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
